Uses of Package
users

  • Packages that use users 
    Package Description
    ai
    The package that contains the classes used in operating the computer players.
    game
    Contains classes that have to do with the actual game of Cards Against Humanity itself.
    ui
    The package that has to do with the user interface for Cards Against Humanity.
    users
    The package that contains the classes that have to do with users, user information, and keeping records on users so that they can be impersonated by the computer.
  • Classes in users used by ai 
    Class and Description
    HumanPlayer
    A class of object that represents real human players.
  • Classes in users used by game 
    Class and Description
    Card_Czar_Exception
    The exception that is thrown when an unnecessary Card Czar operation is performed on a player.
    Player
    A class of object that contains all players including Rando Cardrissian.
  • Classes in users used by ui 
    Class and Description
    Player
    A class of object that contains all players including Rando Cardrissian.
  • Classes in users used by users 
    Class and Description
    Card_Czar_Exception
    The exception that is thrown when an unnecessary Card Czar operation is performed on a player.
    Gender
    A list of possible genders for a user.
    NonRandoPlayer
    A class of object that represents all players except for Rando Cardrissian- both humans and computers.
    Player
    A class of object that contains all players including Rando Cardrissian.
    PlayerTypes
    A list of different types of players.
    User

    UserActionLog
    A class of object that tracks a user's actions in order to discern a pattern of behavior.
    UserBehavior 
    UserGameHistory
